        "generateUrl": "https://portal.azure.com/",
        "setup": "Create an app registration in the [Azure portal](https://portal.azure.com/) under Microsoft Entra ID. Grant the SharePoint or Microsoft Graph application/delegated permissions your integration needs, then acquire OAuth 2.0 access tokens from Microsoft identity platform for the target resource. For SharePoint REST, request a token for your tenant SharePoint resource such as `https://{tenant}.sharepoint.com`; for Microsoft Graph, request a token for `https://graph.microsoft.com`. The SharePoint docs note app-only access via Entra ID requires a certificate for SharePoint CSOM/REST app-only scenarios.",
